data.value: MediStop providing service for the last 15 years all over Bangladesh. A renowned stop for all kinds of medicine. It is open 24/7 and tries to provide excellent service to the consumers.MediStop is a desktop-based application for a pharmacy's billing system built with C#. Different accessibility and functionality for admin and staff users. Profile tab, settings tab, sales report tab, and many more. Microsoft SQL Server used for database management.
